[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 6.6,
    "text": "Yeah, so with the jet engines we could only really get about five minutes full power through them."
  },
  {
    "start": 6.6,
    "end": 9.46,
    "text": "So after doing a couple of runs we had to charge them."
  },
  {
    "start": 9.62,
    "end": 11.14,
    "text": "And during this charging, we had downtime."
  },
  {
    "start": 11.8,
    "end": 13.52,
    "text": "We were waiting around, we were kind of getting bored,"
  },
  {
    "start": 13.98,
    "end": 18.9,
    "text": "just messing around being towed behind the piste and the snowmobile."
  },
  {
    "start": 19.44,
    "end": 22.14,
    "text": "And then I remembered there was actually a Guinness World Record"
  },
  {
    "start": 22.14,
    "end": 25.46,
    "text": "for the fastest speed while being towed by a vehicle."
  },
  {
    "start": 25.88,
    "end": 28.44,
    "text": "And that was set at something around 98 kilometres an hour."
  },
  {
    "start": 28.44,
    "end": 32.28,
    "text": "We asked the piste how fast the snowmobile could go."
  },
  {
    "start": 32.58,
    "end": 34.56,
    "text": "And he said, oh yeah, that can only go about 50, 60."
  },
  {
    "start": 34.68,
    "end": 38.24,
    "text": "But I've got a Mitsubishi Evo. We could do it on that."
  },
  {
    "start": 38.44,
    "end": 40.92,
    "text": "We just thought, as we have this long track,"
  },
  {
    "start": 41.0,
    "end": 43.8,
    "text": "there's a world record being towed behind a vehicle."
  },
  {
    "start": 44.14,
    "end": 46.6,
    "text": "And this man here, who piste-ed everything for us,"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.68,
    "end": 49.12,
    "text": "actually has a nice Mitsubishi Evo."
  },
  {
    "start": 49.3,
    "end": 51.08,
    "text": "We don't know how it's going to go. I might have to let go."
  },
  {
    "start": 51.28,
    "end": 52.24,
    "text": "You know what? That's why we're here."
  },
  {
    "start": 52.28,
    "end": 54.98,
    "text": "We might as well give it a go and see what happens, really."
  },
  {
    "start": 55.88,
    "end": 56.52,
    "text": "Why not?"
  },
  {
    "start": 58.44,
    "end": 62.12,
    "text": "Let's go."
  },
  {
    "start": 62.12,
    "end": 92.1,
    "text": "Let's go."
  },
  {
    "start": 92.12,
    "end": 93.38,
    "text": "Let's go."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.02,
    "end": 116.96,
    "text": "Woo!"
  },
  {
    "start": 116.96,
    "end": 117.34,
    "text": "Woo!"
  },
  {
    "start": 118.7,
    "end": 119.62,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "start": 122.12,
    "end": 123.12,
    "text": "How fast was that?"
  },
  {
    "start": 123.12,
    "end": 129.12,
    "text": "I don't know really because I showed you all the time behind."
  },
  {
    "start": 129.12,
    "end": 132.12,
    "text": "You go in that speed."
  },
  {
    "start": 132.12,
    "end": 133.12,
    "text": "That was crazy."
  },
  {
    "start": 133.12,
    "end": 134.12,
    "text": "Yeah dude."
  },
  {
    "start": 134.12,
    "end": 135.12,
    "text": "Yeah boy."
  },
  {
    "start": 135.12,
    "end": 136.12,
    "text": "That was crazy."
  },
  {
    "start": 136.12,
    "end": 137.12,
    "text": "111.801"
  },
  {
    "start": 137.12,
    "end": 140.12,
    "text": "Did 111 come to the bottom?"
  },
  {
    "start": 140.12,
    "end": 143.12,
    "text": "So we thrashed it."
  },
  {
    "start": 143.12,
    "end": 150.12,
    "text": "We literally just came up with this today."
  },
  {
    "start": 150.12,
    "end": 157.12,
    "text": "He came in his car and we were like that looks like a car we could go fast with."
  },
  {
    "start": 157.12,
    "end": 161.12,
    "text": "And so we were like that's a world record let's try to beat it."
  },
  {
    "start": 161.12,
    "end": 162.12,
    "text": "Done."
  },
  {
    "start": 162.12,
    "end": 163.12,
    "text": "That's good."
  },
  {
    "start": 163.12,
    "end": 164.12,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 164.12,
    "end": 165.12,
    "text": "We're done."
  },
  {
    "start": 165.12,
    "end": 168.12,
    "text": "We reached a speed of 111 km an hour."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.12,
    "end": 169.12,
    "text": "It was amazing."
  },
  {
    "start": 169.12,
    "end": 171.12,
    "text": "Just spontaneous within about 5 minutes."
  },
  {
    "start": 171.12,
    "end": 175.12,
    "text": "I think I'm going to come back again and actually do it properly and see how really fast we"
  },
  {
    "start": 175.12,
    "end": 176.12,
    "text": "get."
  },
  {
    "start": 176.12,
    "end": 177.12,
    "text": "Maybe 150 maybe more."
  },
  {
    "start": 180.12,
    "end": 183.12,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 183.12,
    "end": 191.12,
    "text": "I'm going to get it."
  },
  {
    "start": 191.12,
    "end": 193.12,
    "text": "All right guys."
  },
  {
    "start": 193.12,
    "end": 194.12,
    "text": "See you guys."
  },
  {
    "start": 194.12,
    "end": 195.12,
    "text": "Bye."
  },
